  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide legal support to litigation lawyers</p></li><li><p>Assist in research and the preparation of correspondence, office documents, and legal documents</p></li><li><p>Secretarial and administrative support for the litigation department</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prior experience working as a paralegal-capacity in the litigation department</p></li><li><p>Good command of written and spoken English and Mandarin</p></li><li><p>Meticulous</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and have initiative</p></li><li><p>Familiar with working on the Court's E-Litigation domain<br /></p></li></ul>",
